{
  "stem": "21319.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Laying in-- you know, there was three wooden-- wooden [POLISH], but I don't know how to say it in English, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you sleep like six people on-- and six and six, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three-- I-- we were in the middle, OK?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had every six-- 5 or 6 o'clock, we went on a-- we had to stay there to count us, Appell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the whistle blow, we have to get out and stay outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it's snow or rain or cold, and they used to make us this-- this Nazi woman-- they were-- they were prostitutes who became the-- the Nazi woman-- on-- on woman, you know, in the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were wearing the big black capes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of them got fat like 300 pounds, 200 pounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the meanest bastard there is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They made us jump in the swamps and carry big rocks, you know, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- to suffer, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Food was very, very little because the only food we used to get-- when used to get-- food is only for the transport who came-- went to-- straight to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people had some food with them in the pack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so they used to try give every little in the-- the barracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some food, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and after six weeks and-- yeah, and I-- they made me work in the [GERMAN], it was called, where you pick from the rocks, from the-- from the fallen train-- planes, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a lot of-- because German was losing the war, the Germans, and-- but we didn't know that, but it's-- don't forget, 1944.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had all the shot down planes or helicopters where they were materials, all kind.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
